desc: Established Lines is founded on the design lines and forms established during the mid-century modern era. It all started in NYC's East Village. Established Lines integrates the craft and detail of the best mid-century modern materials and concepts into a line of utilitarian modern furniture.

layout.text: ESTABLISHED LINES INTEGRATES THE CRAFT AND DETAIL OF THE BEST MID-CENTURY MODERN MATERIALS AND CONCEPTS INTO A LINE OF UTILITARIAN MODERN FURNITURE.
